d 'SDLIM': module to rescale variables measured with a limited rating scale
d
d sdlim rescales the standard deviation of a variable such that the
d result is the proportion of the raw standard deviation at the
d maximum standard deviation for a given mean.
d
d KW: data management
d KW: scaling
d KW: standard deviation
d
d Requires: Stata version 11
